# Matchday Masters 26 ⚽

A cross-platform hybrid football/soccer game built with Unity featuring real team names & leagues, custom player creation, immersive career modes, and online multiplayer.

## 🎮 Features

### Core Gameplay
- **Hybrid System**: Switch between management (team tactics, formations) and action (direct player control)
- **Match Engine**: Real-time physics-based football simulation
- **Stadium System**: Stylized global stadiums with dynamic environments

### Career Modes
- **Player Career Mode**: Create a custom player, rise from lower leagues to stardom
- **Manager Career Mode**: Build a dynasty, scout players, manage finances & tactics
- **Real Team Names & Leagues**: Global club system with authentic leagues

### Team Management
- Squad building and customization
- Formations and tactical adjustments
- Player development and training
- Transfer market system
- Contract management

### Multiplayer
- **Online Multiplayer**: Real-time competitive matches (cross-platform)
- **Offline Classic Match**: Quick friendlies, tournaments
- **Leaderboards & Rankings**: Global competitive system
- **Friendly & Ranked Modes**

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Engine**: Unity 2022 LTS+
- **Platforms**: iOS, Android, PC (Windows/Mac), Web (WebGL)
- **Backend**: PlayFab / Firebase
- **Database**: JSON/SQLite
- **Networking**: Netcode for GameObjects

## 📁 Project Structure

Assets/
├── Scripts/
├── Scenes/
├── Prefabs/
├── Art/
├── Data/
├── Audio/
└── Resources/

## 🚀 Quick Start

1. Clone the repository
2. Open in Unity 2022 LTS+
3. Open Scenes/MainMenu.unity
4. Press Play

